coverage:
  output_filter: /\(\d+.\d+%\) covered/`
```

The surrounding '/' is optional.

commit_list.message:
Change expected `coverage` structure for CI configuration YAML file

Instead of using:
`coverage: /\(\d+.\d+%\) covered/`

This structure must be used now:
```
coverage:
  output_filter: /\(\d+.\d+%\) covered/`
```

The surrounding '/' is optional.
